{"tid":2373440,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"人民銀行發「非銀行支付機構條例」 徵求意見稿 ‘非銀行支付’兩大機構最多50%巿場佔有率","createTime":"2021-01-20T12:35:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T03:36:23.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ff78a5ff761595bc4acac74596d4f713ee8d7030","tid":2373440,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T12:35:37.000Z","msg":"該條例詳細規定市場地位支配情形，只要符合1個非銀行支付機構在非銀行支付服務市場的市場份額達到33.33％；2個非銀行支付機構在非銀行支付服務市場的市場份額合計達到50％；3個非銀行支付機構在非銀行支付服務市場的市場份額合計達到60％等其中一種情形，人行可商請國務院執法機構對其採取約談進行預警。<br />\n<br />\n電子支付市場方面，則是符合1個非銀行支付機構在全國電子支付市場的市場份額達到50％；2個非銀行支付機構在全國電子支付市場的市場份額合計達到66.67％；3個非銀行支付機構在全國電子支付市場的市場份額合計達到75％等其中一種情形，人行可商請國務院執法機構進行審查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://turnnewsapp.com/livenews/china/A05624002021012017441332\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fturnnewsapp.com%2Flivenews%2Fchina%2FA05624002021012017441332&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia8dEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=fd2ee5f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://turnnewsapp.com/livenews/china/A05624002021012017441332</a><br />\n<br />\n原文<br />\n<a href=\"https://m6nzwp2vu42j7qm7hibx7ub6aa-adwhj77lcyoafdy-finance-sina-cn.translate.goog/2021-01-20/detail-ikftssan8822553.d.html?from=wap\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm6nzwp2vu42j7qm7hibx7ub6aa-adwhj77lcyoafdy-finance-sina-cn.translate.goog%2F2021-01-20%2Fdetail-ikftssan8822553.d.html%3Ffrom%3Dwap&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia8dEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=03f18be1\" target=\"_blank\">https://m6nzwp2vu42j7qm7hibx7ub6aa-adwhj77lcyoafdy-finance-sina-cn.translate.goog/2021-01-20/detail-ikftssan8822553.d.html?from=wap</a><br />\n<br />\n今日追咗巴巴嘅真係恭喜哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c8e54656169497e23ebc3728ccbfc246cec7839","tid":2373440,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T12:39:06.000Z","msg":"抖音支付在中國上線 主要用於 App 內交易<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cool3c.com/article/159351\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cool3c.com%2Farticle%2F159351&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia8dEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=0ddfe302\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cool3c.com/article/159351</a>"},{"pid":"a6b5c177641a890467a0a4f8e2864f8b47be65b4","tid":2373440,"uid":9974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:09:43.000Z","msg":"驚閪 一早price in左啦"},{"pid":"f0aacbbe00f28779e1fd9b06037ffdda6fe1badf","tid":2373440,"uid":26827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:14:23.000Z","msg":"美股baba都未有事你驚春咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a142b52387ca24ddb5e457081dce98ad87ece2c4","tid":2373440,"uid":40397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:34:30.000Z","msg":"想知佢33.33%,50%,66.67%點計出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce74de261e7c69789d81aa912bdb81e3bdcb27c","tid":2373440,"uid":69563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a142b52387ca24ddb5e457081dce98ad87ece2c4","tid":2373440,"uid":40397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:34:30.000Z","msg":"想知佢33.33%,50%,66.67%點計出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:36:05.000Z","msg":"從官方持有率計算"},{"pid":"feff0ce58ab08c2293ca0f697cda802aa9cb0057","tid":2373440,"uid":119512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a142b52387ca24ddb5e457081dce98ad87ece2c4","tid":2373440,"uid":40397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:34:30.000Z","msg":"想知佢33.33%,50%,66.67%點計出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T03:36:23.000Z","msg":"党話係就係"}]}